    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在连环杀人案中失去生命的主播少女，被以人工智能的形式复原。<br>你需要在管理她的工作的同时，试图找出事件的真相。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/789209c46c05b142231d3bca2c23eae1.webp?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=60 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏主要通过操作“数据集”来推进她的成长。<br>不同的数据集拥有不同的效果，合理的组合数据集让她达到最佳的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/768d43888adf3b3b9bf612fd24f50de1.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >当然，在互联网的世界只有能力是行不通的，你还需要“灵感”来制作视频吸引人们的注意。<br>通过不同的数据集，生成不同的灵感，以打造理想的主播。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/dc42f39ba5ae76bdcab314ea62abe7a2.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >除了互联网的世界，你也可以选择和她一起逛逛真实的世界。<br>在其中遇见的人和事，都能够带给你们灵感与启发。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/2ab9d4d51cafdbd41160fdd88b2a94a5.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在你做好了这一切之后，爱与数字会飞快的上涨。<br>但是对于她本人来说，这样就可以了吗？ </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/43fb684ce7d990e6f344f65eed85dc81.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >至少，幸运的是，这一切将由你来决定。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.poster.avif?t=1771997724\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.webm?t=1771997724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3028730/extras/3f97b1963817a0c86788e3c568392bc3.mp4?t=1771997724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本游戏在研发过程中结合了一定的AI技术支持，如您对此有特殊偏好或顾虑，还请酌情选择是否体验。感谢您的理解与支持。</p></li></ul>",
